{"tid":804532,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"說走就走 高雄～台南","createTime":"2018-09-03T05:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T15:11:37.000Z","uid":72617,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7d1909e347e4c1463510a0476bea0623b83152","tid":804532,"uid":72617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟係一個高雄讀書既澳門人<br />\n今日一訓醒突然想去台南食牛肉湯<br />\n所以就出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有黎台灣既朋友都知道 南部係好撚熱<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/133550_2d22b1287eebf8fa3681f60084a5b126.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F133550_2d22b1287eebf8fa3681f60084a5b126.png&h=94e92c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係乜都冇帶既情況下<br />\n曬死都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n一部老電 銀包 手機 就開始呢個旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先去換個機油先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/133801_ffa8b461957bce0d90b54c40f2139ed3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F133801_ffa8b461957bce0d90b54c40f2139ed3.png&h=67ce38dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去埋7仔買野飲 就真正出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附上路線圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/133909_f960d33b7a40850f8a65bd81b90102f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F133909_f960d33b7a40850f8a65bd81b90102f0.png&h=a5282a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好問我做咩冇文 因為我依家出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1fd1214bf0789bf0282c0d3c90a66fb00d16ca","tid":804532,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"前兩日去完<br />\n周圍都落雨<br />\n啲景點無曬<br />\n嬲9"},{"pid":"7956c24b0276ee51bdfde9e3396629a51580809f","tid":804532,"uid":72617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"da1fd1214bf0789bf0282c0d3c90a66fb00d16ca","tid":804532,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"前兩日去完<br />\n周圍都落雨<br />\n啲景點無曬<br />\n嬲9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"前排南台灣暴雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇水浸算你好彩"},{"pid":"da96e36a7ea9e88e39eda073b3fc12672f3c8dab","tid":804532,"uid":72617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"今次係走台1線<br />\n作為南北高雄嘅主幹道<br />\n係好多紅綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/145130_c646f8970a5ea92ffaacbe4caf80a7bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F145130_c646f8970a5ea92ffaacbe4caf80a7bd.png&h=a35a21cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n渣下渣下 就出左市區<br />\n迎接我嘅係<br />\n望唔到盡頭嘅直線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/145229_a3a9094ed798bd4ea063590f663f02a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F145229_a3a9094ed798bd4ea063590f663f02a6.png&h=0f33f65f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家到左路竹 入左間全家補水<br />\n<br />\n到台南再更新"},{"pid":"a865b348621515448b123e4c582641c534444b15","tid":804532,"uid":72617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"到目的地啦<br />\n台南國華街<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/155837_ec075c630cfd601777b0c7c2ad67f76d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F155837_ec075c630cfd601777b0c7c2ad67f76d.png&h=d567f592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身想食戈間鋪帶開 加上星期一其他鋪都冇咩點開<br />\n行兩轉就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家去左食仙草<br />\n黑工號<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/160001_eb82b1273eeac71d624368a0c30f627a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F160001_eb82b1273eeac71d624368a0c30f627a.png&h=d1b109c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完返高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 平日真係唔適合出去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebea3bd0638b025e114bc17ff032806c20be05d0","tid":804532,"uid":116131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"高雄有咩好玩 嚟緊一個人去5日<br />\n之前未去過 on99 book哂四晚高雄瞓<br />\n之後睇景點自己好似無咩想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36357fe83339ed1410121b26fc3458b20945dcc1","tid":804532,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"留明睇"},{"pid":"3aaf9766474325b77c1888ac00f28c7ed0b11362","tid":804532,"uid":133353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebea3bd0638b025e114bc17ff032806c20be05d0","tid":804532,"uid":116131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"高雄有咩好玩 嚟緊一個人去5日<br /